    "form_header_text": "FY27 Programmatic & Language Appropriations Request Form",
    "form_instructions_text": "PLEASE READ ALL INSTRUCTIONS IN THIS FORM CAREFULLY. EACH YEAR REP. WEBSTER IS UNABLE TO VET SPECIFIC REQUESTS DUE TO INCOMPLETE/INACCURATE SUBMISSIONS. DO NOT SUBMIT YOUR REQUEST TO THE INCORRECT FORM. IT WILL NOT BE CONSIDERED.\n\nInstructions:\n1. This form is for programmatic and language requests only. ONE SUBMISSION PER REQUEST.\nIMPORTANT: THIS FORM IS NOT FOR DEFENSE REQUESTS.\nIMPORTANT: THIS FORM IS NOT FOR COMMUNITY PROJECT FUNDING (CPF) REQUESTS. DO NOT SUBMIT A CPF (EARMARK) REQUEST TO THIS FORM.\n2. Deadlines: The first deadline for requests is March 6th, 2026, and the second deadline is March 13th, 2026.\n3. All required questions on the form must be completed. Incomplete and/or incorrect forms will not be considered.\n4. Word limits on request descriptions and language are set by the Appropriations Committee.\n5. All submitted forms are subject to public disclosure.",
